<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Type-Matching completion</b></p><p>When you need to cast an expression value to the required type, use Type-Matching completion. For example, type</p><span class="code_emphasis"><p>                 String s = (             </p></span><p>and press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:SmartTypeCompletion;</span> to see what happens.</p></body></html>